::Shadow Wing::

She was walking to the forest and heard.  She tuned her ears to hear the 
source of the noise.  She tunes her optics to see through the trees.
She saw Ramhorn walking towards the Arc.  She was hurt and tired.  The last 
thing she wanted was to get into a fight.  She did the best she could to 
stay hidden and kept walking to the Arc.
